flowchart TD
    A[Automated proposal]
    T{Escalate?}
    Q[Human queue]
    R[Approve / edit / reject]
    P[Commit or train]
    A --> T
    T -->|yes| Q
    T -->|no| P
    Q --> R
    R --> P
